rbra-streisand-gracie-abrams@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/barbra-streisand-gracie-abrams@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/barbra-streisand-gracie-abrams@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/barbra-streisand-gracie-abrams@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/barbra-streisand-gracie-abrams@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/barbra-streisand">芭芭拉·史翠珊 (Barbra Streisand)</a>上周末（12 月 14 日）观看格雷西·艾布<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gracie-abrams">拉姆斯 (Gracie Abrams</a> ) 的<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/saturday-night-live"><em>《周六夜现场》</em></a>首秀后，对她大加赞扬。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/gracie-abrams-the-secret-of-us-album-review-3767462">格雷西·艾布拉姆斯 - 《我们的秘密》评论：一种新型的亲密关系</a></strong></li></ul><p>上周六，艾布拉姆斯<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-gracie-abrams-perform-thats-so-true-and-i-love-you-im-sorry-on-snl-3822284">作为音乐嘉宾首次亮相<em>《周六夜现场》</em></a> 。传奇人物芭芭拉·史翠珊（Barbra Streisand）是收看这部长期播出的喜剧小品的众多观众之一，她很快就在社交媒体上分享了对年轻的艾布拉姆斯的想法。</p><p>史翠珊在 Instagram 上写道，并附上了格雷西表演的图片：“我刚刚在本周末的周六晚现场直播中看到了一位出色的新歌手，名叫格雷西·艾布拉姆斯 (@gracieabrams)”。</p><p>她还记下了艾布拉姆斯的血统，对导演<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jj-abrams"><em>J·J·艾布拉姆斯</em></a>大喊：“原来她是我朋友 J·J·艾布拉姆斯的女儿！” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DDpbwJGue_G/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 